dialogueLines: I'm out of a job! Oh why did this happen to me?
What are you looking at, huh? Ever see a guy down on his luck?
What am I supposed to do now? The only thing I got going for me is my long fingers.
Well my record label thought they could just replace me with AI. Now I'll never get to play again.
What? You wanna play... with me?
I thought I'd never get to play again... Let's do it.
